$TTL 1D
@                           IN SOA   nintendowifi.net. root.nintendowifi.net. (
                            42    ; serial (yyyymmdd##)
                            3H    ; refresh
                            15M   ; retry
                            1W    ; expiry
                            1D )  ; minimum ttl

                        1D  IN  NS      nintendowifi.net.

nintendowifi.net.             IN  A       192.168.1.31
*                        IN  A       192.168.1.31
